| Feature             | Tool / Integration                |
| ------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| Bot Logging         | Modify LLaMA backend, Supabase DB |
| SEO Analytics       | Google Search Console API         |
| Load Speed Tracking | Lighthouse CI or Web Vitals API   |
| Charts/Visuals      | Chart.js or Recharts              |
| Hosting             | Vercel (for API/dashboard) + WP   |
| Auth (optional)     | Supabase or Clerk                 |
